<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> busy as a bee • busy as a beehive</xh5><p> <i>busy as a bee</i>—(of a person) full of lively activity; very busy: I don’t have time to talk to you. I am as <u>busy as a bee</u>.</p><p> <i>busy as a beehive</i>—<i>(of an office, shop, etc.)</i> crowded with customers; bustling with activity: The firm was at once as <u>busy as a beehive</u>.</p> </entry>
